Register HUB

java -jar C:\Bhanu\selenium-server-standalone-3.8.1.jar -port 4444 -role hub

hub Address

http://172.16.125.9:4444/grid/register

Register Node

Go to each machine and Trigger command.
 java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver="C:\Bhanu\chromedriver.exe" -jar C:\Bhanu\selenium-server-standalone-3.8.1.jar -port 5001 -role node -hub http://172.16.125.9:4444/grid/register -browser "browserName=chrome,maxInstances=1"
 
